reviewText: I am very happy with this product. As I live in Australia we often don't see the entire of each episode so I really enjoyed watching each episode in full. I am a big fan and the artwork is amazing. Make sure your dvd player can play region 1 dvd's before you buy. Mine is fine so i will definitely be keen to purchase season 3 when and if it is released.
Do you know that you can buy this set on the TLC website for about $30?
